@div sa-gida A

1. [...] X IM u₅ nun diŋir-re-e-ne [...] me šar₂-ra-ba dur₂ ŋar
#lem: X; X; X; u[ride]; nun[prince]; diŋir[deity]; X; me[Being]; šar[numerous]V/i; dur[buttocks]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=A.1

2. {[d]}[nu-nam]-nir en a₂ aŋ₂-ŋa₂ zid-da me gal-gal-la šu du₇
#lem: Nunamnir[1]DN; en[lord]; a[arm]; aŋ[measure]; zid[right]; me[Being]; gal[big]; šu[hand]; du[perfect]
#etcsl: line-id=A.2

3. [a]-a# {d}en-lil₂ ni₂-zu an ki-a pa e₃ ša-ba-ni-e₃
#lem: aya[father]; Enlil[1]DN; ni[fear]; an[sky]; ki[place]; pa[branch]; e[leave]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=A.3

4. diŋir an-na an-na bi₂-su₈-ug mu dug₃ im-mi-in-sa₄
#lem: diŋir[deity]; an[sky]; an[sky]; sug[stand]; mu[name]; dug[good]; še[call by name]
#etcsl: line-id=A.4

5. [...] X KA X lugal-ba igi mu-ni-si-si
#lem: X; X; X; X; lugal[king]; igi[eye]; si[fill]
#etcsl: line-id=A.5

6. [...]-bi NE X ZU
#lem: X; X; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=A.6

7. {d}a-nun-na# diŋir gal-gal-bi igi-zu-uš si mu-sa₂#-e-eš
#lem: Anunak[1]DN; diŋir[deity]; gal[big]; igi[eye]; si[horn]; sa[equal]
#etcsl: line-id=A.7

8. {[d]}en#-lil₂ inim kug dug₄-ga mah-zu-še₃ ŋizzal im-ši-ma-an-ak-eš
#lem: Enlil[1]DN; inim[word]; kug[purify]; dug[speak]; mah[great]; ŋizzal[hearing]; ak[do]
#etcsl: line-id=A.8

9. {[d]}[nu-nam]-nir# an ki niŋin₂-na-bi dili-zu-ni mah-me-en
#lem: Nunamnir[1]DN; an[sky]; ki[place]; niŋin[encircle]; dili[single]; mah[great]
#etcsl: line-id=A.9

10. [...] X {d}a-nun-na-ke₄-ne {ŋiš}rab₃ mah kur-kur-ra
#lem: X; X; Anunak[1]DN; raba[clamp]; mah[great]; kur[mountain(s)]
#etcsl: line-id=A.10

11. [...]-zu su₃-ud en niŋ₂-nam-ma-ni dib dug₄-ga-ni nu-kam₃-me-dam
#lem: X; sud[distant]; en[lord]; niŋnam[anything]; dib[pass]; dug[speak]; kam[alter]
#etcsl: line-id=A.11

12. [...] gal-la-a me-zu me-a dirig a-ra₂-zu niŋ₂ galam-ma-am₃ X nam-kal kur ki su₃-ra₂-še₃ sipad zid-bi# za#-e#-me-en
#lem: X; gal[big]; me[Being]; me[Being]; dirig[make more than]; ara[way]; niŋ[thing]; galam[skilful]; X; namkala[value]; kur[mountain(s)]; ki[place]; sud[distant]; sipad[shepherd]; zid[right]; zaʾe[you]
#etcsl: line-id=A.12

13. a-[a] {d}en-lil₂ ki-ur₃ dur-an-ki šag₄-ge pad₃-da-za
#lem: aya[father]; Enlil[1]DN; Kiʾur[1]; Durankik[1]TN; šag[heart]; pad[find]
#etcsl: line-id=A.13

14. ZU X e₂-kur ki aŋ₂-zu šu-mu-ra-an-du₃ barag mah-zu šu-mu-un-ri
#lem: X; X; Ekur[1]TN; ki[place]; aŋ[measure]; du[build]; barag[sanctum]; mah[great]; ri[impose]
#etcsl: line-id=A.14

15. eš₃-za me-bi me kal-kal-a-am₃ šu-luh zid-bi mah-am₃
#lem: eš[shrine]; me[Being]; me[Being]; kal[rare]; šuluh[ritual cleansing]; zid[right]; mah[great]
#etcsl: line-id=A.15

16. ŋarza-bi kug-kug-ga-am₃ niŋ₂ ka-ge dib-ba-am₃
#lem: ŋarza[rites]; kug[pure]; niŋ[thing]; kag[mouth]; dib[pass]
#etcsl: line-id=A.16

17. e₂-kur-ra šag₄-bi galam# kad₄#-am₃ niŋ₂ lu₂ nu-zu-am₃
#lem: Ekur[1]TN; šag[heart]; galam[skilful]; kad[tie]; niŋ[thing]; lu[person]; zu[know]
#etcsl: line-id=A.17

18. {d}iš-me-{d}da-gan ŋiš-hur me zid-bi si ha-ra-ab-sa₂-sa₂-e
#lem: Išmedagan[1]RN; ŋešhur[plan]; me[Being]; zid[right]; si[horn]; sa[equal]
#etcsl: line-id=A.18

